UPDATE `kin` SET `htmlCodigo_en` = 'The fierce guardian of life, of the ideas and projects that he sets in motion. He is the manager, the producer, the initiator. He enjoys a great existential sensitivity and a unique creativity. If he is not in harmony with himself, he may have many ideas but not carry out any of them because he does not know where to start, or he may also dedicate himself to so many projects at the same time that he cannot fully commit to any of them. Leaving what he starts unfinished energetically delays him. Spiritually, he represents ancestral memory, and if awakened, he manages to integrate it into everything he does' 
WHERE `kin`.`id` = 0;
UPDATE `kin` SET `htmlCodigo_en` = 'It is communication, divine breath, flexibility, and change. It has the gift of speech, so it should be used strategically and with kindness. It needs novelty all the time, tends to be extremely social, although in shadow it can keep much of itself even when surrounded by people and speaking without saying anything. At a spiritual level, it can channel messages from beyond. It needs to focus and express everything it feels deep inside, knowing also when to remain silent.' 
WHERE `kin`.`id` = 1;
UPDATE `kin` SET `htmlCodigo_en` = 'It is the sun of darkness. It represents our unconscious, the dream world, and the ability to realize our dreams. It has the potential to receive messages in dreams; we just have to pay attention to them. It needs a lot of rest and solitude for periods. It is important to know how to also go out and relate to the world, with the spontaneity that characterizes it. They tend to be histrionic, extremely intuitive, and rather stagnate their abundance if they do not believe in themselves. It is important to be attentive to possible craziness, impulsiveness, unresolved desires, and an inflated ego, in order to balance oneself.' 
WHERE `kin`.`id` = 2;
UPDATE `kin` SET `htmlCodigo_en` = 'It is the ability to inject life into everything we propose so that it flourishes, so that it yields results, so that it materializes, and becomes successful. First, the Seed must feel, identify its passions, what it loves to do, so that it can dedicate itself to that and not become unbalanced by expending all its infinite energy on external projects or those it has become accustomed to due to social pressure or just because they work. It is also about dance, joy, pleasure, curiosity, and knowing how to hit the mark, knowing how to wait for the right moment to act.' WHERE `kin`.`id` = 3;
UPDATE `kin` SET `htmlCodigo_en` = 'It is the life force, the cunning to live in the material world, as well as the wisdom to understand that there is no spirituality without physical balance. The Serpent is dedicated to gathering the necessary resources to have a good life; in shadow, that will be its only goal, in light, it will know that this is just the means to evolve in this plane. It tends to be dominant, territorial, and austere, but also very cultured and noble.' WHERE `kin`.`id` = 4;
UPDATE `kin` SET `htmlCodigo_en` = 'It is the bridge between different dimensions. In this plane, it masters the ability to be like a public relations specialist, to create contacts, to know how to relate to others to generate networks and opportunities. In the spiritual plane, it is the messenger of spirits and, although it may block it out of fear, it can receive information for itself or to be transmitted to others as a form of help. Its mission is to understand death as part of life, to deepen its spiritual knowledge about it to know when to let go when necessary.' WHERE `kin`.`id` = 5;
UPDATE `kin` SET `htmlCodigo_en` = 'It represents service, healing, and fulfillment. It is the power to carry out everything one sets out to do. In shadow, the Hand acts just for the sake of doing, addicted to work, but unwilling to risk dedicating itself to what it dreams of the most. In light, everything it does will also be connected to its ability to help and heal. It must be very careful with control and learn to set healthy boundaries between what it gives to others and to itself.' WHERE `kin`.`id` = 6;
UPDATE `kin` SET `htmlCodigo_en` = 'It represents art, beauty, elegance, harmony, creativity, but also abstract thinking, the world of ideas, and intellectual production. Star people enjoy a natural grace, and while their mission is to develop their great creativity, they can easily get lost in the rational realm. In shadow, they seek perfectionism, damaging their nervous system. In light, they can become great and virtuous artists. It is important for them to set aside stubbornness, the need to relativize everything, and the desire to find truth in conceptual thought.' WHERE `kin`.`id` = 7;
UPDATE `kin` SET `htmlCodigo_en` = 'It\'s the world of emotions. The Moon feels everything; her sensitivity is vast, and everything deeply impacts her. In fact, she\'s capable of sensing how everyone around her feels, often wanting to comfort anyone who\'s suffering. This can bring her many problems as she\'ll carry burdens that aren\'t hers to bear. In this regard, she enjoys a powerful intuition and a vivid imagination. She represents the energy of the feminine, the power of the waters, and mastery in relation to the elements of nature. She needs to transcend the drama where she sees it, purify herself of all she feels, and let herself flow.' WHERE `kin`.`id` = 8;
UPDATE `kin` SET `htmlCodigo_en` = 'It\'s the energy of unconditional love. The Dog represents loyalty, fidelity, and companionship; it\'s the guardian of loved ones. In shadow, it has self-esteem issues, always giving too much to those who don\'t reciprocate and demanding in return. In light, it\'s capable of utmost altruism, knowing how to love oneself first, setting healthy boundaries with anything that doesn\'t serve its well-being in relationships, and loving without attachment. It tends to dedicate itself in one way or another to social projects, doing good for humanity. In this sense, it should be careful not to unconsciously act as the savior of others.' WHERE `kin`.`id` = 9;
UPDATE `kin` SET `htmlCodigo_en` = 'It\'s the inner child who, with its wisdom, illuminates the lives of others. In light, it\'s the sense of humor, the playful spirit, the irreverence that questions everything as if playing. In shadow, it tends to take everything too seriously and act as the defender of just causes. It doesn\'t allow itself to relax and holds onto unresolved childhood situations. Its mission will be to show the world that nothing is as solid as it seems and that sometimes it\'s necessary to confront ourselves through laughter to let go of the ego.' WHERE `kin`.`id` = 10;
UPDATE `kin` SET `htmlCodigo_en` = 'It represents the highest standard of integrity. It\'s the wise one who defends just causes, often sacrificing themselves in the process. In light, they are deeply connected to their freedom and will know how to balance their strong need to generate harmony around them with the path they choose to take. In shadow, they may defer to others or fall into acute indecision, not knowing which decisions to make, due to having a rigid concept of what should be.' WHERE `kin`.`id` = 11;
UPDATE `kin` SET `htmlCodigo_en` = 'It\'s the explorer, the seeker of life\'s ultimate meaning. Their main motivation is to know, to know everything, especially about other cultures, territories, knowledge, and idiosyncrasies. In the light, they will know how to be guided by their intuition, and everything they learn will be transformed, to then be shared with the world. In the shadow, skepticism will lead them astray, and they will only seek to know outwardly, lacking the courage to journey within themselves or to find a spiritual path.' WHERE `kin`.`id` = 12;
UPDATE `kin` SET `htmlCodigo_en` = 'It\'s the one who, with their natural charm, manages to transform everything. Artist, performer, alchemist, healer, wizard, engineer, counselor, speaker. In the light, they can fulfill their mission of being a source of inspiration for human beings; in the shadow, pride will lead them to worry only about external validation, about applause.' WHERE `kin`.`id` = 13;
UPDATE `kin` SET `htmlCodigo_en` = 'It represents the panoramic vision, analytical acumen, and cutting-edge creativity. It\'s visionary and very profound, always feeling responsible for the well-being of others. In the light, she will believe in herself to take flight and evolve; in shadow, she will procrastinate, distracting herself with everything her mind can envision, and putting the common good ahead of her priorities as a pretext.' WHERE `kin`.`id` = 14;
UPDATE `kin` SET `htmlCodigo_en` = 'He is the samurai, who with discipline and dedication trains himself to go into battle to win. But the battle is not the conflict; it is the possibility of transforming reality, that which is unjust, in a strategic, fearless, frontal, and above all humble manner. A Warrior in shadow questions everything only out of ego, even himself, sabotaging himself. In the light, he is the spiritual master, low-profile, who illuminates with his actions.' WHERE `kin`.`id` = 15;
UPDATE `kin` SET `htmlCodigo_en` = 'She represents supreme stability. She is the giver of foundation, of structure, both in the physical and in the emotional, psychic, or spiritual plane. They tend to be quite strong individuals who manage to propel, with their great drive, the generation of what is needed to move forward. In shadow, they fall into over-interpretation, being challengers, creating arguments only to validate what they have set their minds on. In light, they know that true stability is to flow with what reality proposes, without pressuring, without resorting to force.' WHERE `kin`.`id` = 16;
UPDATE `kin` SET `htmlCodigo_en` = 'It is the perfect balance, the equanimity, the inner peace that arises thanks to a true acceptance of everything as it is. In light, the Mirror flows with everything without filters or reservations, generating great harmony among those around it. It is one of the seals that usually gets along well with people. In shadow, however, it tends towards extreme judgment, finding no order in anything, least of all in itself, and ends up in crisis by criticizing everything. It is not capable of seeing itself and tends to project its defects onto others. In the traditional Maya calendar, it is associated with the obsidian knife, a spiritual quality to cut off everything that does not serve us in our lives.' WHERE `kin`.`id` = 17;
UPDATE `kin` SET `htmlCodigo_en` = 'It\'s the transformative force of reality. When the storm appears, it\'s time for radical changes, there\'s no other way. In general, it\'s a powerful creative energy, it tends to keep a low profile, but when the time comes, it manifests with great fierceness. In shadow, they stagnate and don\'t allow themselves to change, or conversely, they develop a certain addiction to constant strong movements. They can also remain in extreme introspection, they are very sensitive, and they don\'t show themselves. In light, they manage to create boundary situations to let go of what needed to go and start again at a new level of evolution' WHERE `kin`.`id` = 18;
UPDATE `kin` SET `htmlCodigo_en` = 'It\'s the energy of higher evolution. It represents the life-generating light, wisdom, truth, things as they are. When the Sun appears, it\'s time to shine, to trust who we already are and what we already know intrinsically, and to assume roles of authority, of leadership that correspond to us. It\'s time to face reality as it presents itself, no matter how challenging it may be. The issue with the Sun is that being the truth, it can become uncompromising, radical with ethics, with paradigms, with what it considers right or true, so humility must be worked on above all else. True wisdom isn\'t about showing off, defending, or convincing; it\'s a state of the soul, a permanent connection with our authentic self.' WHERE `kin`.`id` = 19;






--Quiché
UPDATE `kin` SET `htmlCodigo_qu` = 'X\'ak\'bal ri ch\'utinamit, ri yab\'al rech le k\'ux rech k\'utb\'al, ri keb\'anoj rech k\'utb\'al rech li rach\'b\'al. Ri utz awäch, ri ch\'ob\'an, ri ch\'aaj rech rach\'b\'al. K\'ut loq\' ri ruk\'u ri kib\'al ri ulew k\'ay k\'ulaj, xawal li chuxab\' ri k\'ut rech k\'o tzijok ulew chi\' k\'o jun. La ri q\'ij loq\' rech tz\'ijol ri ka\'atzib\'al, ri q\'aik\'atzib\'al, yäqatzib\'al. Xa ri utzawäch ri k\'ut rech wi\', chik\'al ri junan li wi\' q\'ajol rech loq\' rech tzijol' 
WHERE `kin`.`id` = 0;
UPDATE `kin` SET `htmlCodigo_qu` = 'Ri kech rech tzij, ri kech rech rutz\'ijal, ri kech rech tz\'olilal rech k\'ak\'oj. Q\'at k\'utinamit rutz\'ijal, xawi\' ri k\'ut chik\'al tz\'ijol rech wi\' q\'ajol, ti\' k\'utinamit q\'at loq\' rech k\'utinamit la k\'utinamit chik\'al chi\', chi\' rech k\'ut tz\'olilal loq\' rech wi\' ka\' chik\'al ri tz\'ijol. Ri chik\'al ri q\'ajol q\'at chi\' b\'antiox rech utzil, q\'at k\'utinamit chik\'al chik\'al k\'utinamit loq\' chi\' chi\' ri wi\' qajol rech wi\', xawal chi\' xawi\' q\'at chutz.' 
WHERE `kin`.`id` = 1;
UPDATE `kin` SET `htmlCodigo_qu` = 'Ri k\'olb\'al che rutz\'ijal. Xawi\' ri k\'utinamit, ri mundo wuj, rech ri ruk\' ri wi\' tajib\' la\' k\'utinamit chi\'. Q\'at wi\' q\'atatz\'in chi\' rutz\'ijal, k\'u\'wi\' chik ri wi\' la q\'at chawon. Tz\'ib\'itak chik\'al k\'a ri utzil, k\'at ri\' lachinamit la jun chik\'al chik\'ulaj, chik\'al wi\' tz\'a\' k\'utinamit rech ri ruk\' la k\'utinamit. K\'atam chik chik\'al histriónicos, sumamente intuitivos, rech rech ruk\' k\'ut chi\' chik\'ulaj k\'utinamit chik ri\' k\'i\' chi\' ri wi\' rech q\'at loq\' rech k\'utinamit. Utz k\'utinamit wi\' utzij k\'atam rech jun posibles locuras, impulsividades, k\'utinamit k\'i\' loq\' chi\' k\'utinamit, rech chik\'al e\' k\'utinamit, chik jun q\'i\' xkib\'al, k\'u\'wi\' chik ri equilibrarse.' 
WHERE `kin`.`id` = 2;
UPDATE `kin` SET `htmlCodigo_qu` = 'Utzeri wi\' utz\'inb\'el k\'a tz\'ikin ri jun chik chi ri tz\'ak, k\'a k\'umalajal, k\'a b\'anxk\'akal, k\'a wach ri utz\'ijol, chi ri k\'a q\'ij k\'utinamit, chi ri q\'ij k\'u\' xtz\'ib\' wi\' pa k\'u\'k\'axb\'altzi\', chi ri k\'a chi\' xtz\'ikinik chi ri k\'a k\'utinamit, k\'a k\'u\'ri\' rech tz\'ib\'ajil wi\' wi\' tzij. Utz wi\' xtz\'ib\' ri k\'u\'ri\', ri xkik\'inb\'el, ri k\'aq\'ijinb\'el, ri rujwach k\'a wuj wi\' jun, k\'a utz q\'ij k\'aq\'ijinb\'el, k\'a wach ri wi\' winaq k\'ut kik\'ijol.' WHERE `kin`.`id` = 3;
UPDATE `kin` SET `htmlCodigo_qu` = 'Ri wi\' aq\'ij, ri xub\'anil pa utzil ri q\'ijil k\'u\'xanik, xcha\' ri q\'ij pa juyub\'el ri wi\' k\'u\'xanik. Utz xub\'anil chi ri wuj, ri q\'ij rech k\'a wi\' utz rech tzijol k\'u\'xanik q\'ij, chi tz\'ib\'al, k\'a wi\' che rech jun q\'ij rech kik\'ijol pa k\'ik\' xkik\'inb\'el k\'u\'xanik. K\'a k\'utb\'altzij wi\' k\'a q\'ijinb\'el, k\'a paqarab\'al, k\'a xeb\'xk\'utinb\'el, chiq\'echaj, k\'a xchik\'ayutinb\'el rech winaq chi utzijol.' WHERE `kin`.`id` = 4;
UPDATE `kin` SET `htmlCodigo_qu` = 'Ri k\'ab\'al ri k\'utu\'l kik\'otemal chikib\'al ri q\'ij ri juyub\'el. Chik wuj, ri wi\' xkik\'otemal chik ri winaq rech k\'inaqil ri k\'utb\'al, chik chakawil q\'ij, chik xchik\'ay ri winaq chikib\'ij ri awasik chik rech k\'utb\'atz\'ib\' rech utzibalal. Chik wuj k\'u\'xanik, k\'a wi\' k\'u\'xanik rech kik\'otemal ri winaq k\'aq\'alajil, chik ka\'q kik\'otemal ri k\'utu\'l ri q\'ij q\'ab\'ijal k\'u\'xanik k\'a ri k\'utu\'l rech rutz\'in ri winaq k\'a wi\' chik\'ayibalal k\'u\'xanik rech atiq chik ta kiwi k\'ij.' WHERE `kin`.`id` = 5;
UPDATE `kin` SET `htmlCodigo_qu` = 'Ri awäch ri k\'ik, ri q\'ij, y ri xk\'ajol. K\'a wi\' ri q\'ij rech tikonel ri chik\'ajol k\'a winaq rutzijil kub\'anoq. Chik wuj, ri awäch rech tikonel xk\'ik ri k\'ik kub\'anoq, kiwäch rech xqatäqil ri chik\'ajol, b\'e ri chik\'inb\'al ri a xk\'utij kiwi\'. Chik winaq ruk\' ri k\'ik rech ri ri\' xk\'utij kub\'anoq ri\' ri q\'ij, rech ri ri chik\'ajol chik\'ayij k\'a k\'olal chik\'ajol k\'a winaq rech k\'at sachat.' WHERE `kin`.`id` = 6;
UPDATE `kin` SET `htmlCodigo_qu` = 'Ri ri ak\'awal, ri winaq, ri ak\'aslemal, ri armonía, ri q\'ijalaj, käch ri ajch\'isal kub\'anoq, b\'e k\'a ri ri q\'ij ri chik ri k\'ut winikaj chikin chik\'ajol, chi k\'ut k\'aslemal ri le k\'i\'ix ri k\'u\'l ri k\'i\'ix q\'ijalaj, b\'antä chi rech ri k\'u\'l k\'o ri xkib\'al rech ri ak\'aslemal rech ri q\'ij. Chik winaq ujun wi\' ri winaq q\'ij, ri winaq chik\'ajol, b\'antä rech chik k\'u\'l k\'o k\'olal chi rech k\'i\'ix, ri winaq chik\'ajol rech k\'ut b\'anoj. K\'a tijox winaq chik ulew chi\' chi\' k\'o\'olal, ri k\'i\'ix ri k\'o ri q\'ijalaj, b\'e ri chik\'ajol ri wi\' ri k\'u\'l.' WHERE `kin`.`id` = 7;
UPDATE `kin` SET `htmlCodigo_qu` = 'E li ri k\'aslemal ri awäch. Ri Ruk\'uk\'ulew chik ri k\'aslemal, xk\'ux kib\' chik, b\'antä xk\'ux wäqil chik. Chik ajanel ri k\'aslemal rech k\'ut wan taq k\'o ri winaq k\'utäj, chi riwäch ta\' achawäch ri k\'ot. Xkib\'aj chik tijox chi\' rech winaq, chi winaq chik ajch\'umal ri kib\'äl che\' ri b\'anoj ri xk\'ux kib\'äl. Chik nimaq tijox ri energia k\'ak\'ik\', ri winaq che\' ri poder ri k\'ak\'ik\', b\'e ri k\'aslemal rech k\'ut kib\'äl ri jun ch\'umil rech ri le k\'i\'ix ri chik\'ajol. K\'utz xuquje\' taq k\'o ri tijox k\'ot, chi purificar k\'u\'l chik\'ajol rech k\'ut nimaj tz\'ikin, b\'e xche\' ri tijox xkib\'aj.' WHERE `kin`.`id` = 8;
UPDATE `kin` SET `htmlCodigo_qu` = 'E ri k\'utb\'altzij ri k\'amor ch\'uti\'. Ri Tz\'i\' ri b\'anoj, riqaj laj b\'a\' k\'ut, ri q\'ij, y riqaj laj k\'ut. Rech xk\'utemajol re, chi k\'utal ri winaq chiq\'ui\' chi k\'ulew, chi akajol k\'ut ri winaq ri wach, che\' winaq k\'u\'nimal rech k\'ut. Rech chi wi, k\'utemajol k\'ulew chik, k\'utemajol chik ri k\'amor ri wi k\'ut chik, ri\'aj chi\'ut k\'utab\'äl ri b\'a ri xcha\' ri wi k\'amor ch\'uti\' chi rech taqajol re ri winaq xk\'utik. Q\'eqetaj rech xk\'ulew xkatun re ri\' winaq xewaq. Rech chi wi, q\'eqetaj rech xk\'utijonik chik la q\'ij ulew k\'utb\'altzij chik.' WHERE `kin`.`id` = 9;
UPDATE `kin` SET `htmlCodigo_qu` = 'E ri\' q\'ij b\'i k\'ut rech chi k\'utemajol chik la ri b\'anoj xchiq\'ui\'. Rech chi wi, k\'utemajol rech k\'ut la yala\' ri chik, la awa\'l, la chwäch\' k\'ut xch\'upk\'ij ri b\'i chi rech chwäch\'oj chik. Rech chi winaq taqi\', k\'utemajol xk\'utk\'uch ri b\'i ri xcha\' chiq\'ui\' la xch\'utk\'uch. Rech chi b\'anoj chi\' wi, chi b\'i\' taq k\'ut q\'eqetaj k\'ut la wachaj chi\'ut chik y chi winaq la winaq chiq\'ui\' chi awa\'l. Ri\'aj chi chik chik chik k\'ut rech k\'utemajol chik ulew xchiq\'ui\' ulew chik ri b\'i xcha\' ulew.' WHERE `kin`.`id` = 10;
UPDATE `kin` SET `htmlCodigo_qu` = 'Rech taq k\'ut k\'utb\'alaj chik taq awal rech chi q\'eqemajal b\'i\'. Rech chi winaq k\'utemajol rech chi k\'o\'j wi, xecha\' chi b\'anoj chik b\'i chik, k\'ut qach\'ab\' chik rech chi b\'i. Rech chi wi, taqi\' rech b\'i\' xk\'utk\'uch k\'ut wi k\'utemajol chik k\'u rech winaq chik xk\'utk\'uch ulew chi\'ut chik rech k\'utemajol chik b\'i ri\'. Rech chi b\'anoj, rech qach\'ab\' k\'u xkib\'äl rech b\'i k\'u rech xk\'utb\'äl ajinaj rech chi k\'utemajol b\'i\', b\'i\' ri k\'ut taq xkib\'äl k\'u chi k\'u\'x chi rech k\'utemajol k\'ut chi.' WHERE `kin`.`id` = 11;
UPDATE `kin` SET `htmlCodigo_qu` = 'Rech chi k\'ajolaj, rech chi q\'eqemajol ri b\'i\' chik wi k\'ut rech ri b\'i\' ri\'. Ruk\'u\'x k\'ut b\'i\' k\'ajolaj wi k\'ut, k\'ajolaj chik taq b\'i\' k\'u rech k\'utemajol, k\'u xkib\'äl, k\'u xk\'ajolaj, chik k\'u xk\'utemajol ri b\'i\'. Rech chi wi, taqi\' k\'utemajol rech chi\'uk\' ri k\'ut k\'ut k\'u wi k\'ut, chik taq k\'ut xkib\'äl b\'i\' k\'u k\'u xkib\'äl, b\'i\' ri rech k\'utemajol ri chik. Rech chi b\'anoj, rech b\'i\' qach\'ab\' k\'u rech xkib\'äl ajinaj k\'ut ri b\'i\' chik wi k\'ut chik, xewitzel k\'u ri k\'utemajol b\'i\' chik wi k\'ut chi b\'anoj.' WHERE `kin`.`id` = 12;
UPDATE `kin` SET `htmlCodigo_qu` = 'Rech ri k\'ut ri\' k\'utemajol rech ri ri\' ta k\'u xk\'utemajol ri b\'i\' chik. Ri\'atz\'ib\'al, ri\'malaj, ri\'k\'utnäch, ri\'xk\'ajolaj, ri\'maj b\'i\', ri\'winaq, ri\'tz\'utuj, ri\'jak\'aq. Rech chi wi, chi k\'u\'xk\'utemajol ri rech b\'i\' ta k\'u ri k\'ut ri\' k\'u\'xk\'utemajol ri winaq, chik taq chi\'uk\' chik wi k\'u k\'u k\'ut b\'i\' k\'u b\'anoj.' WHERE `kin`.`id` = 13;
UPDATE `kin` SET `htmlCodigo_qu` = 'Rech ri xk\'otik ri\'chiq\'aj, ri\'wak\'ib\' ri\'wi\' ri\'k\'utemajol ri b\'i\' chik. Ri\'k\'otikaj wi, chiri ch\'umil, chi winaq chik k\'u ri q\'ij k\'ot xk\'otikaj, chik ri\' ch\'umil rech chik chi k\'utemajol ri b\'i\' rech winaq, chik taq ri\' k\'u ri\' xk\'otikaj, chi rech b\'i\' rech ri\'wi\', chik k\'ajol ri\'xk\'utemajol ri k\'i k\'ut ri\' yinak.' WHERE `kin`.`id` = 14;
UPDATE `kin` SET `htmlCodigo_qu` = 'Ri\'k\'iche\' k\'ot, ri\' re k\'ot samurai, chi ch\'ajij k\'u ri tijonel chik taq ri k\'otol, k\'u chiri k\'otol, k\'u b\'i\' ri xk\'otol rech k\'u ri k\'otol, b\'i\' ri k\'otol k\'u chi xk\'otol xk\'utinaj, xk\'ulew, xa k\'i\'wi\', xa k\'i\'ikaj k\'ab\'ajel ri k\'u\' rech k\'u xk\'utinaj. Ti rej k\'otol ri\'xk\'utinaj chiri k\'ot, ti ch\'ab\'ab\' k\'u ri k\'ot, xk\'utinaj k\'u k\'i\', xk\'utinaj k\'u aj ch\'utemajal, k\'u aj k\'ajol k\'u tijonel chik.' WHERE `kin`.`id` = 15;
UPDATE `kin` SET `htmlCodigo_qu` = 'Ri rutz\'ij ri e wach chiwäch. Chi ri taqawäch, ri wuj, xk\'utinaj ri wäch, ki\' rej k\'a ri tzukub\'aj chi k\'otol chik ri k\'otol wi, xk\'utinaj ki\' rej k\'a ri tak\' k\'u k\'otol, ri uq\'ijil, utz\'ijil, k\'u k\'otol k\'ajol k\'u wuj. Ti chiri\' xk\'utinaj, chi k\'otol wuj, chiri ta chik k\'ajolaj k\'u rech, ta k\'u ch\'ok ri k\'otol rech, xk\'utinaj ujol wi\' chi wakax ri k\'u ch\'ok. Ti wi\' chiri, chi ri k\'otol xk\'utinaj k\'u q\'eqi\', k\'u ri k\'otol tzukub\'aj rech wi\', ta\' wi\' k\'a\' ri k\'i\' ri k\'otol k\'u wach, k\'u utz\'ijil.' WHERE `kin`.`id` = 16;
UPDATE `kin` SET `htmlCodigo_qu` = 'Ri b\'anojil wi\', ri k\'akajay, ri wäch k\'i\' ri kajib\' wi\' xk\'utinaj ta ch\'ut ri xk\'ot ri wuj chik ri k\'otol k\'u q\'eqi\' rech. Ti wi\' ri k\'u q\'eqi\' ta\' xk\'utinaj ri Xb\'alamuk\' wi\' chi wach wuj wi\' rech ri\' k\'u q\'eqi\' rech xk\'utinaj utz\'ijilaj k\'u utz\'ijil rech chik ri k\'otol k\'u chik. Ta k\'u wach uwi\' rech xk\'utinaj k\'u k\'i\' ri k\'otol k\'u wach. Ta\' ri k\'otol uqijil chik ri k\'u q\'eqi\' rech k\'u utz\'ijilaj k\'u k\'i\' ri k\'otol k\'u wach, chik ri q\'eqi\' rech. Ta\' ri wuj k\'u k\'otol maya k\'i\' xk\'utinaj uch\'ab\'al xk\'ajolol, ki ri\' q\'eqi\' rech ta\' utz\'ijilaj k\'u wuj chik ri wach k\'u k\'otol rech' WHERE `kin`.`id` = 17;
UPDATE `kin` SET `htmlCodigo_qu` = 'E ri k\'anal ch\'ut ch\'oy. Rech xk\'atun ri tempestad, chi wi xk\'ot xchinku\' chi k\'u\'j, ma chik xewaq k\'ulew. Xecha wi k\'utb\'altzij q\'ij, chi ajk\'ub\' ri b\'anoj, chik\'a chik\'uxul, ba\'q\'ij xk\'ot xchinku\' chi winaq xk\'ot, che\' chik\'uxul. Rech xk\'ut re ri b\'anoj, k\'atunajol chik, k\'utemajol chik, jok\'ojol k\'utu\'x. Rech chi wi, che\' chik\'ajol ri xtreme k\'umal, ma chik. Ma k\'ulew, chik b\'a ri ki\'che ch\'umil k\'utuj ri chik ri aq\'ab\'äl rech a\' ri aq\'ab\'äl rech a\' chik\'ajol ri wi kib\'äl.' WHERE `kin`.`id` = 18;
UPDATE `kin` SET `htmlCodigo_qu` = 'E ri energia k\'anal ch\'ut a\' k\'ulew. Chik ri ruk\'ux k\'utuj, ruk\'ux, k\'utb\'altzij, a\'b\'anel ri kib\'äl che\' ri q\'ij. Rech xk\'atun ri q\'ij, chi wi k\'ab\'ij, chik ri a\' winaq chikaj chi wi a\' kib\'äl rech chi wi a\' kib\'äl, che\' kib\'äl che\' chik\'ajol, chib\'äl chik\'ajol ri xub\'inal. Rech xk\'atun ri realidad chi k\'ot xchinku\' chi k\'u\'j, chi xti\' taq xkoj rech. Ri problema xk\'ut b\'e ri ruk\'ux chi ri q\'ij, chi k\'ulew rech winaq chik ajanel ri k\'u\'xul, k\'u\'xul chi wi, k\'u\'xul che\' a\' che\' b\'anel ri aq\'ab\'äl, ri chik\'ajol ri b\'anoj che\' ri q\'ij ri k\'o ri a\' wi che\' k\'ut. Ri b\'anel ri k\'utb\'altzij ma k\'utuleje\', ma chik\'ajol, ma k\'utwalij, xechawin taq, ri q\'ij rech ajk\'ub\' chikaj ri wi a\' kib\'äl.' WHERE `kin`.`id` = 19;

--Kaqchickel
UPDATE `kin` SET `htmlCodigo_kq` = '<span>Ja ri tata’ k’aslemal ri b’anob’äl, ri tzijob’äl yal b’an pa jalojil. Ja ri b’anol, ri xeb’anoxib’al, ri xerujil. Kuxo jun ch’umilal kik’aslemal chiqamik yal kikotemab’äl. Man xkikotem ke wach’ik ri tinamit k’o man xkikotem junam ruwäch xujchaj jun tzij ruwäch pa yalan ya’ ru ruk’ wäch pa k’ut. Xb’ano pa yalan xujchaj wi yal k’o yujunam rumal k’o, man xb’ano wi pa tajin k’o ruwäch ri tinamit. Ri k’aslemal k’o yal kik’aslemal rumal man xb’ano xutikij junam. Ruwi’ ri nimalaj k’aslemal yal kik’aslemal chik.</span>\n' WHERE `kin`.`id` = 0;
UPDATE `kin` SET `htmlCodigo_kq` = '<span>Ri k’ulb’il, ri q’aq’alal k’aslemal, ri xub’an yal ri tajin k’o. K’o jun nima’j b’anik, re xkojik k’ul ri b’an pa b’ixan yal ri tzalu’. Kik’in ronojel ri jalojil, k’o jun chik’aj wi chi keb’ix k’ulik. Man xkotzij ke wach’ik ri k’aslemal, man xub’i’ ke wach’ik pa taq jay, man xb’ano ri k’aslemal, k’o junam ri ruwi’ ri nimel xb’an chik, xb’ano pa ka ri tinamit yal b’an pa jalojil jas. A ri ruk’u’x ruwi’ xb’ano pa k’ul ri tzij pa jun nimaq’ij. Kik’in pa ka ri k’aslemal yal kik’otem ri b’anob’äl k’o xuk’u’x pa ka k’as, kikotemik man xb’ano ri xaqan ri tzalu’.</span>\n' WHERE `kin`.`id` = 1;
UPDATE `kin` SET `htmlCodigo_kq` = '<span>Ri q’ij ri k’aslemal. Xb’anob’äl ri kik’aslemal ch’umil, ri nimanel pa tzijob’äl yal ri k’o ri saqch’ool k’o ri b’anob’äl. K’o jun nima’j k’ul pa ka xb’ano ri tzij pa tzijob’äl, k’o pa k’ulik xkojik. Kik’in pa k’as k’ulil yal kik’otem ri k’aslemal. Ri k’ulik xkotzij pa k’ul k’o yal b’anob’äl, kik’ul ri xak’amowik kik’inomik. Xb’an pa ka kikotemik jay, xb’an xik’ulik jun ch’umil k’ul, yal ri kik’aslemal xkojik. K’o jun nima’j tzijonemil, jun ch’ab’äl junam xb’ano chik, man xkojik ri kik’aslemal pa ka ri kik’as. Ri k’ulik xkotzij pa k’ul jun nimel chi k’amik, chi kik’in chik, jun nimel chi ruwäch tzij, yal jun q’aq’al k’aslemal pa ka k’o xajo’ chik.</span>\n' WHERE `kin`.`id` = 2;
UPDATE `kin` SET `htmlCodigo_kq` = '<span>Ri k’ulik pa k’o xajo’ chik ri b’anob’äl pa k’ul ri k’o yal kik’in jaloj, pa k’o yal kik’o ri k’o, pa k’o yal kik’ul yal kik’ulunem. Ri jaloq’ij kik’in pa k’o chik’aj, kikotem ri b’an pa ka ri kik’in yal kik’o, ri k’o yal kik’aj k’o, pa k’o yal kik’in ri k’o yal kik’otem chik, man kik’o ri k’aslemal pa ka kik’o jun nima’j b’anob’äl ri jun ruwäch kik’aslemal, man kik’o chik pa ka kik’in chik ri kik’aslemal ri kik’in yal kik’o ri nimqak’ij xajonem pa tajin yal kik’o junaj. Xb’an pa ka kik’o ri b’i, ri k’a’ k’ul, ri k’aslemal, ri xik’in yal kik’otem, yal kik’in ch’ab’äl pa k’o jun xuk’u’x pa k’ul k’o ri qak’altäq chi k’amik pa k’ul k’o.</span>\n' WHERE `kin`.`id` = 3;
