UPDATE `energia` SET `htmlCodigo_en` = '<p>Principle of Unity.</p>\n<p>Purpose, Attract, Unify.</p>\n<p>The principle and origin, the human being as a whole.</p>\n<p>Unity establishes purpose, object, and goal of action no matter how small it may be.</p>\n<p>Unity is the whole, the only absolute truth, it is the mental creation of the whole.</p>\n<p>In the circle of perfection, all beings are inseparably united regardless of their dimension of manifestation. The belief that it is not so creates a crack in the original relationship, and that crack in the energy field creates a polarity (as a healing process) that must become vibration.</p>\n' WHERE `energia`.`id` = 1;
UPDATE `energia` SET `htmlCodigo_en` = '<p>Principle of Polarity.</p>\n<p>Challenge, Stabilize, Polarize.</p>\n<p>Skeleton and essence, Masculine and feminine; they form the dual generative principle, the dual symmetry of beings. They are the extremes of the same phenomenon, identical opposites in their nature: spirit and matter, light and darkness, yin and yang.</p>\n<p>Harmonizing vibration is resolving polarity by balancing the two extremes, that is, including them.</p>\n<p>If everything is light, forms blur, which is why the contrast of shadows is necessary.</p>\n<p>Cultivating our resonance is harmonizing our vibration with higher resonances such as planetary, solar, and galactic ones.</p>\n' WHERE `energia`.`id` = 2;
UPDATE `energia` SET `htmlCodigo_en` = '<p>Principle of Rhythm or Compensation.</p>\n<p>Service, Unite, Activate.</p>\n<p>Flow and ebb, ascent and descent, action and relation; it is the movement between the poles of all planes (physical, mental, and spiritual).</p>\n<p>Every phenomenon, every process has its own rhythm: everything has a beginning, is born, grows, dies, and is reborn. Precious liquid that gives warmth and energy to the body, blood, the water of nature, rain.</p>\n<p>By creating polarities, we trigger events, circumstances that we experience and overcome. The actions that produce a field of negativity (ignorance, spiritual darkness) are karmas; the actions that suppress and correct the negativity (wisdom) are Dharmas and create a beneficial field.</p>\n' WHERE `energia`.`id` = 3;
UPDATE `energia` SET `htmlCodigo_en` = '<p>Principle of Measurement.</p>\n<p>Form, Measure, Define.</p>\n<p>The four as a measure of all material structures (the pyramid), always enters into relationship with the triune composition of the spiritual, forming the Septenary structure of all that Is.</p>\n<p>The power of the mathematical ordering of the macro and microcosmos. Everything that exists is according to the measure of the law of the whole.</p>\n<p>It establishes the limits of structures; the 4 main forces, 4 sacred directions, 4 elements: heat, wind, and water over earth. There are four Mayan regions, 4 elementals, 4 nucleotides, 4 primary chemical elements, 4 cosmic races, cardinal directions, solar seasons, personality chakras, etc.</p>\n' WHERE `energia`.`id` = 4;
UPDATE `energia` SET `htmlCodigo_en` = '<p>Principle of the Nuclear.</p>\n<p>Splendor, Command, Empower.</p>\n<p>The capacity for realization, the mobility of the fingers, perceiving the beauty of nature, the 5th point or center of the Universe.</p>\n<p>Every unit, no matter how small, objective or subjective, has a nucleus as an attractor and a periphery of manifestation (the nucleus of the atom and electrons, for example).</p>\n<p>The conception of the chromatic hue of five derives from it, which is the action of the fifth galactic force; the hue of color gives the intonation.</p>\n' WHERE `energia`.`id` = 5;
UPDATE `energia` SET `htmlCodigo_en` = '<p>Principle of Organic Balance: 2x3. (Polarity through Rhythm)</p>\n<p>Equality, Balance, Organize.</p>\n<p>The polarity of rhythm generates the organic principle, the law of the Hexagonal ordering of crystalline and cellular structures. The tendency of structures linked to the process of life is to reach relative equilibrium, an intermediate state of realization, from which to continue movement towards higher consciousness.</p>\n<p>The principle of Potential Difference provides the resolution of situations through qualitative leaps between states of energy. Nothing that happens is casual, everything is subject to the power of the primordial law; every effect has its cause and at the same time is causal of other effects, the First Central Cause is the Creator.</p>\n<p>Its action is to balance, the principle of integration of our introspection.</p>\n' WHERE `energia`.`id` = 6;
UPDATE `energia` SET `htmlCodigo_en` = '<p>Principle of Mental Unification. (Mystical Power)</p>\n<p>Harmonization, Inspire, Channel.</p>\n<p>We are resonant units within a Mental whole; the material order is a fractal of the mental ordering of the universe. We do not control the mind; we are thought by the mind, living immersed in it.</p>\n<p>The seven channels energy by inspiring harmonization. It represents the lunar phases of 7 days, the second step of inner transformation; the active, restless intellect, the lunar influence.</p>\n' WHERE `energia`.`id` = 7;
UPDATE `energia` SET `htmlCodigo_en` = '<p>Principle of Harmonic Resonance. (Resonant Octaves)</p>\n<p>Integrity, Shape, Harmonize.</p>\n<p>Just as in music, scales occur in octaves, vibrational energies contact and resonate with their respective counterparts at higher and lower levels of manifestation, as well as with the secondary harmonics derived from vibration.</p>\n<p>Octaves are the vehicle of information of the whole, as the law of harmony; the tone eight grants the ability to shape, to mold, to describe aspects of the immediately higher level of vibration.</p>\n<p>Eight is the inner essence, the being as a receptacle of cosmic essence, the 2 times NAHUI (4), combines the 4 directions (+) and the 4 corners (X) of the world.</p>\n' WHERE `energia`.`id` = 8;
UPDATE `energia` SET `htmlCodigo_en` = '<p>Principle of Cyclical Periodicity.</p>\n<p>Intention, Accomplish, Pulse.</p>\n<p>Everything that moves does so according to Cosmic Law; cyclical periodicity, not the repetition of events, is the quality by which an event is associated with others both preceding and succeeding it in time as resonant phenomena (cycles within cycles).</p>\n<p>It represents the feminine aspect of the generative principle (Yin), the creative pole in which the generation or production of new forms, energies, and concepts that drive the evolutionary process of life, the objective, manifest; the intention to set action in motion.</p>\n' WHERE `energia`.`id` = 9;
UPDATE `energia` SET `htmlCodigo_en` = '<p>Principle of Manifestation.</p>\n<p>Manifest, Produce, Perfect.</p>\n<p>Movement as energy manifests at each level or octave of vibration (dimension); everything that manifests, that is, that becomes present (objectively or subjectively) can be measured, and vice versa.</p>\n<p>The manifestation of energy on all planes involves overcoming or facing the obstacles inherent to the dimensional plane and the type of presence to be manifested. Hands together, the duality of hands (5+5=10), balancing each other, like an arrow to the target.</p>\n' WHERE `energia`.`id` = 10;
UPDATE `energia` SET `htmlCodigo_en` = '<p>Principle of Dissonant Structures.</p>\n<p>Liberation, Dissemination, Dissolution.</p>\n<p>All structures, regardless of their nature, tend to enter new realities; perpetual movement implies mutation and constant change, in life we become aware of these new realities.</p>\n<p>The structures that \"disorder\" as an apparent chaos to the material world are actually entering another higher order not understandable from the three-dimensional perspective. The crack that splits us from the whole is non-evolution, our tendency to stay sheltered where we feel comfortable and safe is an illusion; a higher order that we currently assimilate as chaos awaits our entry, it is the fifth dimension that transcends the previous ones.</p>\n' WHERE `energia`.`id` = 11;
UPDATE `energia` SET `htmlCodigo_en` = '<p>Principle of Complex Stability: 2x6.</p>\n<p>Cooperation, Universalize, Dedication.</p>\n<p>It is the polarization of organic balance, through which each species gains its own level of harmonic frequency, that is, its status as a species: code, niche, habitat, etc. It generates the conservative forces of living organisms, including the earth, as symbiotic cooperation.</p>\n' WHERE `energia`.`id` = 12;
UPDATE `energia` SET `htmlCodigo_en` = '<p>Beginning of the universal movement or principle of vibration.</p>\n<p>Presence, Transcendence, Permanence.</p>\n<p>Everything that exists is in perpetual motion, from the most subtle vibrations to the densest and heaviest expressions of low frequencies, to the point that these extremes appear at rest.</p>\n<p>Movement is the energy that flows from the source and returns to it. This principle grants transcendence to everything that operates with and obeys the law of one; transcendence is the quality of enduring beyond time and space. The total union of all preceding numbers, the last number represents internal knowledge, introspection, centrality, and transparency, Wisdom of the Universe, Mother Earth, respect for what exists, flourishes, and bears fruit.</p>\n' WHERE `energia`.`id` = 13;

